media:group.media:title: What are NUMBERS?
media:group.media:description:
What are numbers?

Numbers are parts of the very fabric of our reality.  But what are they? How does the brain percieve them? Are our numbers unique? Watch the video to find out!

Answering the questions that no one asks, Kinertia brings you closer to the world as you know it!
